pois.name: Poets
pois.descrh: Situated in a bright and airy building in the residential area of Battery Park City and near the Hudson River, this reading room is an open resource for all ages, with a 70,000-volume library, as well as reading, and other poetry-centric events.
pois.descrc: This is a place where people can go to read, write, and learn about poetry. It is a quiet and peaceful place where people can relax and enjoy the beauty of poetry. People like to go there to read their favorite poems, to learn about new poets, and to meet other people who love poetry.
